some cowboy shit.

21:16.811 --> 21:19.278
He's not gonna like a fed
closing down a local business

21:19.347 --> 21:20.346
without going through him.

21:20.414 --> 21:21.948
And that's it?
That'll do it?

21:22.016 --> 21:24.550
Yeah. I mean, it's gonna
rein him in a little bit.

21:24.618 --> 21:26.752
But...really,
if I were you,

21:26.821 --> 21:29.688
I'd think about giving the DEA
what they want.
Yeah.

21:29.690 --> 21:31.289
If I were you,
I'd do your goddamn job

21:31.291 --> 21:33.459
if you want
to keep getting paid.

21:36.965 --> 21:43.702
