[ Chuckles ]

23:48.896 --> 23:50.263
Here you go.

23:52.700 --> 23:54.700
Get that regular popcorn,
though.

23:54.769 --> 23:56.835
None of that cheddar shit,
right?

23:56.904 --> 23:59.171
And some Bonkers!
Get me some Bonkers.

23:59.239 --> 24:00.239
Andrew:
Okay.

24:01.175 --> 24:03.910
Look, sorry about the cash.
I paid my mom's rent today.

24:03.978 --> 24:06.378
Forgot to swing by the bank
afterw--
All right. Shut up.

24:06.447 --> 24:08.314
Take those ridiculous pants
off.

24:15.323 --> 24:17.323
