24:26.600 --> 24:29.668
It's pretty messed up,
taking a kid from his dad.

24:29.670 --> 24:32.572
Well, we don't know
what's really going on.

24:35.409 --> 24:37.343
J:
What's going on at your bar?

24:37.411 --> 24:39.478
I went over there earlier
looking for you,

24:39.480 --> 24:40.680
and it was closed.

24:43.083 --> 24:44.016
