24:49.023 --> 24:51.423
Pope:
DEA guy?

24:51.492 --> 24:52.891
Yeah.
I guess the, uh, feds

24:52.893 --> 24:54.693
didn't even go through
the Oceanside PD.

24:54.762 --> 24:56.762
