or Russia

26:02.763 --> 26:04.096
wants to buy a house in L.A.

26:04.164 --> 26:06.098
or finance a yacht,
skip paying his taxes.

26:06.166 --> 26:07.433
What do they do?

26:07.501 --> 26:09.835
You're thinking
there's another guy

26:09.904 --> 26:12.504
that does what
your liquor store guy does,

26:12.573 --> 26:14.841
but it's bigger.

26:14.909 --> 26:16.375
Exactly.

26:16.444 --> 26:19.378
