without people knowing.

34:46.020 --> 34:47.820
Like, uh, javelinas?

34:47.889 --> 34:50.289
You're talking about
a hawala.

34:50.357 --> 34:51.290
Yeah.

34:51.358 --> 34:52.825
So, you know any?

34:52.893 --> 34:56.963
And I mean big ones who are
sitting on a lot of cash.

34:59.033 --> 35:04.470
What you're talking about --
It's dangerous.

35:06.641 --> 35:08.974
[ Door closes ]

35:09.043 --> 35:11.410
[ Birds crying ]

35:13.514 --> 35:15.648
What the hell, man?

35:15.716 --> 35:18.183
Everybody out of here.
Go!
Oh, hey, man.

35:18.185 --> 35:19.384
Uh, you want to play?

35:19.386 --> 35:21.787
No.
Craig said it was cool.

35:21.856 --> 35:23.122
Yeah.
Craig's an idiot.

35:23.190 --> 35:26.125
Get out of here. Go.
Everybody leave.

35:27.928 --> 35:29.328
Hey, can you drive us home?

35:29.396 --> 35:32.465
No!
Go back to school or something!

35:32.533 --> 35:33.933
Go!

35:37.872 --> 35:39.872
God damn it.

35:43.278 --> 35:45.478
[ Door closes ]

35:54.355 --> 35:56.689
[ Cellphone buzzing ]

36:01.095 --> 36:02.761
Hello?
Who's this?

36:02.830 --> 36:05.698
I talked to our friend.
I think I found a solution.

36:05.766 --> 36:07.099
Yeah?
And what's that?

36:07.168 --> 36:10.102
Look, I'm gonna need to
present it to all the Codys.

36:10.171 --> 36:11.904
In person, okay?

36:12.840 --> 36:14.239
Why?

36:14.241 --> 36:15.774
'Cause your brother shows up
here saying one thing,

36:15.843 --> 36:17.910
and then your nephew shows up
saying another thing.

36:17.979 --> 36:19.879
I got to know
everyone's on board.

36:20.781 --> 36:21.914
Uh, okay.

36:21.983 --> 36:25.918
Um...my bar,
10:00 a.m. tomorrow morning.

36:25.987 --> 36:28.587
No.
In two hours.

36:28.655 --> 36:30.122
What do you mean,
two hours?

36:30.191 --> 36:31.524
Things are already
in motion.

36:31.592 --> 36:33.592
So just call your brothers
and J.

36:33.661 --> 36:35.794
Two hours.

36:35.863 --> 36:38.064
[ Cellphone clicks ]

36:40.335 --> 36:44.003
It's all set.
They'll all be there.

36:44.071 --> 36:45.204
Sure we need all of them?

36:45.272 --> 36:46.739
You want to put pressure
on one Cody,

36:46.807 --> 36:50.543
you got to get the other Codys
to do it.

36:50.611 --> 36:52.945
And you think they will.

36:53.014 --> 36:57.750
I've been working these guys.
They only care about themselves.

36:57.818 --> 36:59.752
None of them are going to jail
for Adrian Dolan.

36:59.820 --> 37:01.187
I promise you that.

37:02.823 --> 37:05.691
See you in two hours.

37:05.760 --> 37:10.329
♪♪

37:14.001 --> 37:17.003
Your body is so soft...
supple.

37:17.071 --> 37:19.338
Like a --
Like a cheetah.

37:19.407 --> 37:25.011
I mean, no spots, but...
so smooth.

37:25.079 --> 37:26.745
Shut up.

37:26.814 --> 37:28.347
[ Exhales deeply ]

37:28.416 --> 37:29.548
Mm.

37:29.617 --> 37:30.683
Andrew:
Mom!

37:30.751 --> 37:32.018
Oh, shit.

37:32.086 --> 37:33.886
No.
No, not yet.

37:33.954 --> 37:35.221
Mom?

37:35.289 --> 37:37.890
[ Exhales deeply ]
Get dressed.

37:37.958 --> 37:39.157
Shh!
Come on.

37:39.227 --> 37:41.760
[ Mid-tempo rock music playing ]

37:41.829 --> 37:45.598
You expect me to put my pants on
with this?

37:47.368 --> 37:49.635
Hey.

37:49.704 --> 37:51.637
Where are the snacks?

37:52.773 --> 37:53.972
What happened?

37:53.974 --> 37:55.908
Hey. Tell me.

37:55.976 --> 37:57.309
The scary man.

37:57.378 --> 37:59.645
What happened?

37:59.714 --> 38:02.415
He wanted to
buy us soda.

38:03.918 --> 38:05.984
What else?
Come here.

38:05.986 --> 38:08.087
What else?

38:10.458 --> 38:12.591
He said
you owed him money.

38:12.660 --> 38:15.261
Anything else?

38:15.329 --> 38:18.064
He said if you don't pay him
his money,

38:18.132 --> 38:20.799
he's gonna take us
to live with him.

38:20.868 --> 38:23.002
Hey. Hey.

38:24.472 --> 38:26.272
All right.
Don't worry about it.

38:26.340 --> 38:29.408
You're here now.
You're safe.

38:29.477 --> 38:31.009
Hey.

38:31.011 --> 38:32.878
Stop.
Listen to me.

38:33.748 --> 38:36.148
Wipe away your tears.
[ Thudding in distance ]

38:36.216 --> 38:39.885
You look like
a drowned rat.

38:39.954 --> 38:41.420
Got the TV hooked up.

38:41.489 --> 38:45.223
Yeah. Go play with Mr. Billy.
He's nice.

38:45.225 --> 38:47.826
Yeah.
Let's go watch some Muppets.

38:47.895 --> 38:49.561
[ Thudding continues ]

38:49.630 --> 38:51.497
Andrew, stop!

38:51.566 --> 38:53.900
Stop.

38:53.968 --> 38:56.034
Listen to me.

38:56.904 --> 39:01.107
You know that feeling that you
have in your chest right now?

39:01.175 --> 39:03.909
Like a ball of fire burning
in your belly?

39:03.978 --> 39:06.712
Hm?

39:06.781 --> 39:08.681
I have it, too.

39:09.850 --> 39:11.317
Don't worry.

39:12.186 --> 39:17.923
That man is never
gonna bother us again.

39:17.992 --> 39:23.329
♪♪

39:23.397 --> 39:25.931
[ Air hissing ]

39:26.000 --> 39:27.866
What, they took the kegs,
too?

39:27.868 --> 39:29.402
Yeah.
They took everything.

39:32.340 --> 39:34.072
You get any sleep?

39:34.142 --> 39:37.143
Yeah.
I took a power nap.

39:37.211 --> 39:39.878
So, what's Chadwick got?

39:39.880 --> 39:41.480
I don't know.

39:41.549 --> 39:44.150
He just said for us all
to meet here.

39:46.955 --> 39:49.021
Well, I spoke to Frankie.

39:49.089 --> 39:52.625
She said she might know a couple
of those hawala dudes.

39:52.693 --> 39:53.826
Good.

39:53.894 --> 39:56.628
I didn't think you heard
anything we said.

39:56.697 --> 39:58.231
Yeah.
Well, you thought wrong.

40:05.840 --> 40:06.739
[ Door closes ]

40:10.110 --> 40:13.112
What the hell
is this about?

40:15.716 --> 40:20.086
Well,<i> this</i> is your last chance
to save your pathetic ass.

40:21.189 --> 40:23.856
My friend here says
that we should talk.

40:23.924 --> 40:29.862
♪♪

40:29.930 --> 40:32.665
$2.6 million.

40:32.733 --> 40:35.333
That's how much
my investigation's cost so far.

40:35.335 --> 40:38.270
Plus three years
of my life.

40:38.339 --> 40:40.339
You took that from me.

40:40.341 --> 40:42.208
No, we didn't take shit
from you.

40:43.678 --> 40:47.280
Adrian Dolan was the key witness
in my op.

40:48.949 --> 40:50.783
And I want him back.

40:51.686 --> 40:54.754
Mm.
Can't help you there.

40:55.423 --> 40:58.691
You can.
And you will.

40:58.759 --> 41:00.426
Or you'll be the one
doing the time.

41:00.494 --> 41:04.496
If you had anything on us,
we'd be in custody already.

41:04.565 --> 41:07.499
What I have is a local cop

41:07.568 --> 41:11.704
that you dumbasses thought
you could turn.

41:11.772 --> 41:14.573
What I have
is a federal-state relationship,

41:14.575 --> 41:17.443
which means I have
an endless ocean of shit

41:17.511 --> 41:20.213
that I can dump on your heads.

41:22.383 --> 41:25.918
I made a phone call.
Your bar got raided.

41:25.986 --> 41:28.421
Another call next week,
it's your house.

41:30.190 --> 41:33.559
And your dead mother's house.

41:35.329 --> 41:37.430
And your dead brother's house.

41:39.199 --> 41:42.134
And your bowling alley.

41:42.202 --> 41:44.803
[ Chuckles ]

41:44.805 --> 41:48.641
Aw, you guys
ain't seen nothing yet.

41:51.145 --> 41:55.081
Liquor board, Oceanside PD,
state cops --

41:55.149 --> 41:57.550
I work with 'em all.

41:57.618 --> 41:59.886
And I will bring
every one of them down on you

41:59.954 --> 42:02.354
until the end of time.

42:02.423 --> 42:08.026
♪♪

42:08.096 --> 42:10.930
Mnh-mnh.
Don't look at him.

42:12.032 --> 42:14.833
Look at me.

42:14.902 --> 42:17.035
'Cause I'm the one who's gonna
be in your nightmares

42:17.105 --> 42:19.071
every night.

42:19.974 --> 42:22.040
I'm the one who's gonna be
haunting your --

42:22.042 --> 42:23.676
[ Shell clangs ]

42:26.046 --> 42:27.980
[ Exhales deeply ]

42:28.048 --> 42:30.783
Dude never shuts up!

42:35.123 --> 42:37.790
Honest truth --

42:37.858 --> 42:40.192
I didn't know he was pulling
that liquor-board shit.

42:40.260 --> 42:43.529
But...that's when it hit me.

42:43.598 --> 42:45.664
He was never gonna stop.

42:45.666 --> 42:48.200
I mean, he -- he would've gotten
all the local agencies,

42:48.269 --> 42:49.868
IRS, immigration.

42:49.937 --> 42:53.806
This guy was seriously pissed
about that Adrian business.

42:53.874 --> 42:55.874
That's the problem
with these true-believer types.

42:55.876 --> 42:59.412
They're just...a bit much.

43:01.281 --> 43:03.482
God damn it, man.

43:03.551 --> 43:05.751
Chadwick:
What?

43:05.820 --> 43:08.287
You asked me to do something,
so I did.
Yeah. No.

43:08.356 --> 43:10.489
Not -- Not this.

43:11.692 --> 43:13.025
I had to get him out here
somehow,

43:13.093 --> 43:14.961
so I told him
I've been working you guys

43:15.029 --> 43:18.697
and, uh...
that I wanted to be a fed.

43:18.699 --> 43:21.900
[ Laughing ]
You should've seen his face.

43:21.902 --> 43:25.237
I mean, he practically came
in his skivvies.

43:25.305 --> 43:30.576
I think I've, uh, proven
my usefulness to you guys.

43:31.712 --> 43:34.313
This kind of service comes
at a higher price.

43:35.916 --> 43:40.553
Five grand.
Two grand a month going forward.

43:44.325 --> 43:46.058
Great.

43:46.126 --> 43:48.861
Oh, his car's outside.
We drove separately.

43:48.929 --> 43:52.264
I saw him put his keys
in his pocket.

43:52.332 --> 43:54.667
And the gun's a burner.

43:54.735 --> 43:58.136
But, um,
I think I'll keep it safe.

43:58.206 --> 44:00.339
Just in case.

44:02.877 --> 44:12.018
♪♪

44:14.488 --> 44:18.925
♪♪

44:21.562 --> 44:30.903
♪♪

44:30.971 --> 44:40.413
♪♪
